Package edu.lehigh.cse216.jub424.backend.data_structure

Class User

java.lang.Object
edu.lehigh.cse216.jub424.backend.data_structure.User
public class User extends Object
User holds information of one user. Because we will ultimately be converting instances of this object into JSON directly, we need to make the fields public. That being the case, we will not bother with having getters and setters... instead, we will allow code to interact with the fields directly.
